name: Helping Hands
description: We strive to prevent dogs from ending up on the street with our spay/neuter program. We educate the public about the importance of spay/neuter and provide free and low-cost procedures.We will be working to rescue stray and abandoned dogs through an active adoption program, spay/neuter initiative, and educational campaigns. Helping Hands is not just a rescue organization, we are a vibrant community of advocates, dog-lovers, and change-makers who envision a kind and compassionate future.
